    <div class="faq-a" id="can-hybrid-ai-content-rank-in-google-ai-overviews"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes. Google AI Overviews now appear in 25.8% of US searches. Hybrid content with structured H2s, FAQ schema, lists, and tables earns up to 26.9% more AI Overview citations than unstructured content. The hybrid loop in this guide already produces those structures by default.</p></div></div>
